01:50:36,003 --> 01:50:38,627
[SPEAKER_18]: Simon Alcindor, 404 Tainter Street.

1072
01:50:39,448 --> 01:50:44,796
[SPEAKER_18]: I was just wondering, I know you mentioned the whole meeting, was that after the final BNRD mappers release?

