[SPEAKER_10]: Someone tells me to stop.

1385
02:10:45,408 --> 02:10:46,549
[SPEAKER_10]: I want to get them all done.

1386
02:10:47,350 --> 02:10:47,611
[SPEAKER_02]: Okay.

1387
02:10:47,851 --> 02:10:47,931
[SPEAKER_02]: Yeah.

1388
02:10:47,951 --> 02:10:48,572
[SPEAKER_02]: All right.

