1515
02:19:32,048 --> 02:19:34,049
[SPEAKER_02]: Having the affirmative, none of the negative, the motion passes.

1516
02:19:35,173 --> 02:19:40,057
[SPEAKER_02]: All right, 2-6-0-6-1, submitted by Mayor Brianna Lugo-Kern, fiscal year 2027 budget submission.

1517
02:19:43,028 --> 02:19:57,461
[SPEAKER_02]: Dear President, mayors and city councilors, pursuant to Mass General Law chapter 44, section 32, I respect the request and recommend that your honorable body approve the proposed fiscal year 2027 general fund budget, public educational and governmental peg access special revenue fund and water and sewer enterprise fund budget.

1518
02:19:57,481 --> 02:20:00,564
[SPEAKER_02]: The total submitted appropriation for all departments, including schools is $217,375,456.13.

1519
02:20:00,604 --> 02:20:01,645
[SPEAKER_02]: And I think that's for the general fund.

1520
02:20:09,392 --> 02:20:23,839
[SPEAKER_02]: And then we have to meet these appropriations, the sum of 216,624,203 dollars and 81 cents be raised and appropriated from the fiscal year 2027 tax levy and other general revenues of the city and that 108,750 dollars be transferred from the sale of cemetery lots and 208,759 dollars and 44 cents be transferred from cemetery perpetual care funds and 353,742 dollars and 88 cents be transferred from the casino mitigation fund.

1521
02:20:39,793 --> 02:20:41,235
[SPEAKER_02]: The PEG special access fund at $276,101.97.

1522
02:20:41,315 --> 02:20:43,497
[SPEAKER_02]: Further, that $276, that amount be funded by revenue from cable access fees.

1523
02:20:43,517 --> 02:20:45,519
[SPEAKER_02]: And finally, the water sewer enterprise fund budget at $30,030,904.68.

1524
02:20:58,972 --> 02:21:02,297
[SPEAKER_02]: and that be funded by anticipated revenue of the Water and Sewer Enterprise Fund.

1525
02:21:02,337 --> 02:21:03,899
[SPEAKER_02]: Thank you for your kind attention to this matter.

1526
02:21:03,959 --> 02:21:06,482
[SPEAKER_02]: Sincerely, Brianna Lungo Kern, Mayor.

1527
02:21:07,584 --> 02:21:11,489
[SPEAKER_02]: Thank you Madam Chief of Staff for being here, for presenting the budget.

1528
02:21:13,498 --> 02:21:16,239
