1800
02:50:03,278 --> 02:50:13,685
[SPEAKER_01]: Legislative $25,000 for the constituent services assistant that the council has been discussing and presented, and we've had some lengthy discussions on, both here and

1801
02:50:15,653 --> 02:50:18,238
[SPEAKER_01]: through you, Councilor Mullane, with our human resources director.

1802
02:50:18,599 --> 02:50:27,757
